# Documentation Navigation

This directory contains the complete documentation foundation for Dictate-to-Clipboard.

---

## Directory Structure

```
/docs/
  /meta/               ← Start here! AI agent guidance & orientation
  /overview/           ← Product summary, glossary
  /specification/      ← Requirements (UC, FR, NFR, data structures)
  /architecture/       ← System design, components, contracts, risks
  /adr/                ← Architecture Decision Records (numbered)
  /iterations/         ← Implementation roadmap (8 iterations)
  /testing/            ← BDD seeds, test strategy, test infrastructure
  /changelog/          ← Version history and planning
```

