## Documentation Principles

**Stable IDs:**
- Once assigned, IDs (UC-###, FR-###, etc.) should not change
- Deprecate and create new if significant change needed

**Traceability:**
- Every implementation traces back to a requirement or ADR
- Update `specification/traceability-matrix.md` when adding code

**AI-Friendly:**
- Short sections, scannable lists, clear hierarchy
- Explicit acceptance criteria ("AC:") in user stories
- BDD scenarios tagged with @Iter-N, @UC-###, @FR-###

