## When to Read What

**Before starting implementation:**
→ Full context load (all of the above)

**Before starting a new iteration:**
→ `iterations/iteration-{N}-*.md`
→ Referenced FR/NFR/UC files
→ Referenced ADR files

**When debugging:**
→ `architecture/runtime-flows.md`
→ `architecture/risk-register.md`
→ Relevant ADR files

**When writing tests:**
→ `testing/bdd-feature-seeds.md` (find @Iter-{N} scenarios)
→ `testing/test-strategy.md`

**When requirements are unclear:**
→ Check referenced FR-### in `specification/functional-requirements.md`
→ Check ADR-#### for constraints
→ Ask user if still ambiguous

