## Common Patterns

**Find a requirement:**
```bash
Grep: "FR-012" in specification/functional-requirements.md
```

**Find which iteration implements a feature:**
```bash
Read: specification/traceability-matrix.md
```

**Find BDD scenarios for an iteration:**
```bash
Grep: "@Iter-3" in testing/bdd-feature-seeds.md
```

**Understand a design decision:**
```bash
Read: adr/0000-index.md
Read: adr/0002-cli-subprocesses.md
```

**Load iteration dependencies:**
```bash
Read: iterations/dependency-graph.yaml
```

